ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I recommend it, and ISS can give a much better explanation of what Grand Strategy is than I can.
There is nothing I would recommend more highly than the Grand Strategy course. It is truly an unrivaled foundation for building intellectual capital.
If you get in there is absolutely no reason not to take it - you will get a lot out of the course.
I would but I would inform the student the extent of the work required.
A very rigorous course that is well worth it.
Good class, don't expect a life changing experience, but the summer project should be good at least.
This is a great course- I highly recommend it.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course was the driving force behind my accumulation of knowledge in the discipline. It has been truly pivotal in my development.
Very much enhanced my knowledge of history, especially as a non history major.
